  <brief_title>Randomized Control Trial on Postoperative Weight Bearing After High Tibial Osteotomy (HTO)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Study on Postoperative Weight Bearing After Opening Wedge High Tibial Osteotomy (HTO): Early Weight Bearing Versus Delayed. Open Labelled Randomized Clinical Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
